import React from 'react';
import { Form, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';
import UseForm from './useForm';
import FormValidate from './formValidate';

function formSignUp() {

    const { handleChange, values, handleSubmit } = UseForm(FormValidate);
    return (
        <Form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
            <Form.Group controlId="formName">
                <label htmlFor="username">Name</label>        
                <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Enter name" name="username"   value={values.username}  onChange={handleChange}/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formEmail">
                <label htmlFor="useremail">Email address</label>
                <input type="email" id="useremail" placeholder="Enter email" name="useremail"   value={values.useremail}  onChange={handleChange}/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formPassword">
                <label htmlFor="userpass">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="userpass" placeholder="Password" name="userpass"   value={values.userpass}  onChange={handleChange}/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formPasswordConfirm">
                <label htmlFor="userpassconf">Confirm Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="userpassconf" placeholder="Confirm Password" name="userpassconf"   value={values.userpassconf}  onChange={handleChange}/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formCheckbox">
                <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
            </Form.Group>
            <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                Submit
            </Button>
        </Form>
    )
}

export default formSignUp;
